content:
Been reading up on this fake news stuff that seems to be so prominent recently. 

I mean, come on, who actually falls for fake news!

By the way, thought I'd share this with you guys. 

Pretty big news I saw on my facebook feed. 

Super Mario coming to PS4!!!!!!! WOW!,pic.twitter.com/AvzFik2BgD

Seems Sony will bring one of their games to Nintendo consoles according to my facebook news feed.

Here is an image of Uncharted 4 on Wii U.,pic.twitter.com/eQNbDGHcZD
nice, but at least photoshop the disc to say "wii u" instead of ps4.
I think you missed the joke.
:( will try to be better at it next time.
People fall for it all the time.  There's many canadians dumb enough to believe Trump called us snow mexicans for example lol
we elected Donald Trump and you're asking who falls for fake news?
it really is amazing what some people believe
how can I be game of the year edition if it never had dlc
at least 50% of those who voted in the u.s. Election this month...
but fake news is just so much more interesting than real news!
IS YOU READING ABOUT FAKE NEWS FAKE? I AM SO CONFUSED.
